Academic Papers
	1.	Scarfone, K., & Souppaya, M. (2013).
Guide to Enterprise Patch Management Technologies.
National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST), SP 800-40 Rev. 3.
Link: https://csrc.nist.gov/publications/detail/sp/800-40/rev-3/final
Summary: This publication outlines best practices for vulnerability and patch management in enterprise environments, emphasizing continuous scanning, prioritization, and remediation. It provided context for how automated vulnerability assessment tools fit into a larger security lifecycle.
Used in: Vulnerability Management and Risk Assessment Module

